### BambooHR API Direct Tests
### Use these to investigate API responses directly
### Replace YOUR_COMPANY and YOUR_API_KEY with actual values

@domain = YOUR_COMPANY
@baseUrl = https://{{domain}}.bamboohr.com/api/v1
@apiKey = YOUR_API_KEY

### ============================================
### EMPLOYEE ENDPOINTS
### ============================================

### Get Employee Directory
GET {{baseUrl}}/employees/directory
Authorization: Basic {{apiKey}}:x
Accept: application/json

### Get Single Employee (all default fields)
GET {{baseUrl}}/employees/123
Authorization: Basic {{apiKey}}:x
Accept: application/json

### Get Single Employee with Specific Fields
# Note: Use field names from /meta/fields endpoint
GET {{baseUrl}}/employees/123?fields=firstName,lastName,email,jobTitle,department,Skills,customSeniority1
Authorization: Basic {{apiKey}}:x
Accept: application/json

### Get Employee Files
GET {{baseUrl}}/employees/123/files/view
Authorization: Basic {{apiKey}}:x
Accept: application/json

### Get Employee Table Data (Job Info)
GET {{baseUrl}}/employees/123/tables/jobInfo
Authorization: Basic {{apiKey}}:x
Accept: application/json

### Get Employee Table Data (Compensation)
GET {{baseUrl}}/employees/123/tables/compensation
Authorization: Basic {{apiKey}}:x
Accept: application/json

### Get Employee Table Data (Employment Status)
GET {{baseUrl}}/employees/123/tables/employmentStatus
Authorization: Basic {{apiKey}}:x
Accept: application/json

