### ============================================
### CUSTOM REPORTS (POST)
### Use for data not available via standard endpoints
### ============================================

### Custom Report - Employee Birthdays
POST {{baseUrl}}/reports/custom?format=JSON
Authorization: Basic {{apiKey}}:x
Accept: application/json
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Employee Birthdays",
  "fields": ["displayName", "firstName", "lastName", "dateOfBirth", "department"]
}

### Custom Report - All Employee Data with Custom Fields
POST {{baseUrl}}/reports/custom?format=JSON
Authorization: Basic {{apiKey}}:x
Accept: application/json
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Employee Data Export",
  "fields": [
    "displayName",
    "firstName",
    "lastName",
    "email",
    "jobTitle",
    "department",
    "location",
    "hireDate",
    "status",
    "Skills",
    "customSeniority1",
    "teams"
  ]
}

### Custom Report - Training Certifications
# Note: Add your custom training field names here
POST {{baseUrl}}/reports/custom?format=JSON
Authorization: Basic {{apiKey}}:x
Accept: application/json
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Training Certifications",
  "fields": [
    "displayName",
    "department",
    "AZ-900: Microsoft Azure Fundamentals - Completed",
    "AZ-104: Microsoft Azure Administrator - Completed",
    "AWS Certified Cloud Practitioner - Completed",
    "KnowBe4 Security Trainings - Completed"
  ]
}

